OL,3,CEuston station's marble columns 'would
OL,4,Cfall off' without bands, minister
OL,5,Cadmits
OL,7,FHe said: "The station itself was very
OL,8,Fmodern in 1968. It is no longer very
OL,9,Fmodern.
OL,11,F"As a previous chair of Network Rail,
OL,12,FI can tell you that if you look
OL,13,Fclosely in the columns in the station,
OL,14,Fthere are bands round the marble
OL,15,Fbecause it would fall off without
OL,16,Fthem. It is no longer in fit
OL,17,Fcondition."
