OL,7,FLord Hendy, who is also a former
OL,8,FTransport for London commissioner,
OL,9,Ftold peers in Westminster about the
OL,10,FGovernment's 100-day rapid improvement
OL,11,Fplan for the station and hopes for the
OL,12,Flonger term.
OL,14,FHe said: "I would like to take some
OL,15,Fmodest credit for having re-included
OL,16,Fthe concourse at Euston into the
OL,17,Foverall plan for the development of
OL,18,FEuston and, now that the tunnels for
OL,19,FHS2 will go there, I am very hopeful
OL,20,Fthat all parts of the station will be
OL,21,Ffit for passenger usage in the future.
OL,26,@vD@JOU
