OL,7,F"In the meantime, the most important
OL,8,Fparts of the 100-day plan are these:
OL,9,Fthe concourse is too small, so the
OL,10,Flogical thing to do on the concourse
OL,11,Fis to load the trains earlier, and yet
OL,12,Fthe position up until very recently
OL,13,Fwas that neither of the train
OL,14,Fcompanies was routinely managed there
OL,15,Fto do that, but they are now changing.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
