OL,5,Cadmits
OL,7,F"So a significant proportion of Avanti
OL,8,Ftrains will be loaded at least 20
OL,9,Fminutes before departure and, for the
OL,10,Fmore local services on the London
OL,11,FNorthwestern trains, platforms will be
OL,12,Ffull of passengers even before the
OL,13,Ftrain has arrived.
OL,15,F"That will make a huge difference.
OL,17,F"There is a bookshop which is there
OL,18,Fcurrently but won't be there shortly
OL,19,Fto create some space.
