OL,7,F"I can recall we got criticism for
OL,8,Fremoving Boots, but actually too many
OL,9,Fshops and not enough concourse space
OL,10,Fis not the right answer.
OL,12,F"And there will be some further
OL,13,Fimprovements to signage and visibility.
OL,15,F"At least, when the last signage was
OL,16,Fdone it was hoped to be the right job,
OL,17,Fbut I'm afraid it turned out not to
OL,18,Fbe."
